膠子彈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:50:10.000Z","msg":"如果警察真係咁都真係痴撚咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}